Winter Season Sales EDA¶

In [449]:
start_date10 = '2017-11-01'
end_date10 = '2018-02-28'

start_date20 = '2018-11-01'
end_date20 = '2019-02-28'

start_date30 = '2019-11-01'
end_date30 = '2020-02-28'

start_date40 = '2020-11-01'
end_date40 = '2021-02-28'
In [450]:
mask10 = (df['Date'] > start_date10) & (df['Date'] <= end_date10)
mask20 = (df['Date'] > start_date20) & (df['Date'] <= end_date20)
mask30 = (df['Date'] > start_date30) & (df['Date'] <= end_date30)
mask40 = (df['Date'] >= start_date40) & (df['Date'] <= end_date40)
In [451]:
df_winter_2017 = df.loc[mask10]
df_winter_2018 = df.loc[mask20]
df_winter_2019 = df.loc[mask30]
df_winter_2020 = df.loc[mask40]
